Module org.nasdanika.graph
Package org.nasdanika.graph.processor

Annotation Type Processor

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(METHOD)
public @interface Processor
    Annotation for a method creating an Element processor. The method shall have zero or one parameter. In the second case the parameter type shall be assignable from ProcessorConfig or its subclasses - NodeProcessorConfig or ConnectionProcessorConfig. An annotated method may return an object or null. In the first case the returned object may be introspected to wire handlers and endpoints to methods and fields with annotations.
    Author:
    Pavel
